{"tid":1631900,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[人權法] 過與不過 應該唔關香港示威激烈程度事","createTime":"2019-10-06T16:34:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T16:44:35.000Z","uid":141793,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3665e89209c187577d4b3150900098e47ee7377e","tid":1631900,"uid":141793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:34:24.000Z","msg":"老實講 我之前都好擔心有機會唔過<br />\n但其實有幾個學者都話實過<br />\n(因為美國同中國已經反枱 香港牌係一張好牌）<br />\n<br />\n當然我覺得有隱憂係美帝忘記左無人理上唔到Senate 不了了之 或者 成為美中貿易戰 成交既一部分<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但最後我唔覺得香港示威激烈與否 會有影響<br />\n作為一個外國人都係食花生 難聽啲講 香港亂反北京  佢地睇戲會唔開心咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"432fb73a792c1341097c514774433ce8907c39ce","tid":1631900,"uid":141793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:37:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a38023a0e2fc2f14d67c391728dcf3f923919a3","tid":1631900,"uid":141793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:40:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a27dd7bfdab1a05ce7636dffb68b286a301fa50d","tid":1631900,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:42:17.000Z","msg":"【警世良言】中共劇本係想抹黑「香港人打砸搶燒」，然後種族滅絕！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1623758\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1623758</a><br />\n<br />\n毛澤東：西藏越亂越好，可以鍛鍊軍隊，可以鍛鍊 基本群眾，又為將來平叛和實施改革提供充足的理由<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530340\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530340</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家要冷靜, 理性分析, 我地唔可以變成中共口中既暴徒</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我地要外國幫手先可以贏, 佢地全部人都係左膠, 所以畫面要做好啲, 唔好咁多裝修, 要多裝飾<br />\n<br />\n中共<span style=\"color: red;\">無理</span>出老解, <span style=\"color: red;\">8964</span>, 之後被國際制裁<br />\n中共<span style=\"color: red;\">合理</span>出老解, <span style=\"color: red;\">新彊</span>, 然後就沒有了然後"},{"pid":"aa18e1a7cf1f0bce9b2825700cd66e53f6b888a0","tid":1631900,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:44:35.000Z","msg":"佢地係大國, 要有合理制裁中國, 所以我地要做好睇啲<br />\n佢地唔係中共依一類既小人"}]}